{"tid":18008,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉兆佳：中央有意改善政治環境 減少因選舉引起鬥爭","createTime":"2016-12-02T05:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T05:16:33.000Z","uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60abd1befceef6169010b6b48840ac224daa6ff2","tid":18008,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:12:05.000Z","msg":"「幫港出聲」召集人周融表示，中央同意無回鄉證的反對派申請證件入內地。身兼政協的全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳認為，此舉是釋出善意，表示中央正在調整對香港的政策，以更包容及和諧的手法處理香港事務，希望爭取港人對中央的信任，並促使反對派轉變對中央的立場。<br />\n劉兆佳說可能因為選舉臨近，將於社會引起更多政治鬥爭，中央在這情況下釋出善意，表示有意改善香港政治環境，某程度上可以減少因選舉引起的鬥爭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8A%89%E5%85%86%E4%BD%B3-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83-%E6%B8%9B%E5%B0%91%E5%9B%A0%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E9%AC%A5%E7%88%AD-095932937.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258A%2589%25E5%2585%2586%25E4%25BD%25B3-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2596%2584%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%2592%25B0%25E5%25A2%2583-%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%259B%25A0%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E7%2588%25AD-095932937.html&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPBpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=7d9d4d21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8A%89%E5%85%86%E4%BD%B3-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83-%E6%B8%9B%E5%B0%91%E5%9B%A0%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E9%AC%A5%E7%88%AD-095932937.html</a>"},{"pid":"1264712e8cdaf03b54dab4ee7f12eb6605da9a46","tid":18008,"uid":47042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:16:33.000Z","msg":"幾時發宇宙通行證？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}